  <!-- Algae Oil Separation -->
  <h2 id="algae-oil-separation">Algae Oil Separation</h2>

  <p>
    An algae <a href="/oil-centrifuge/">oil separation centrifuge</a> separates the algae oil from water. This centrifuge is a disc-stack industrial centrifuge that continuously exerts high force to separate the light oil from the water.
  </p>
  <p>
    A self-cleaning centrifuge also separates the algae cell debris from the oil and self-ejects this separated biomass intermittently.
  </p>

